x1270--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MTS-Tory-Lanez-@-2000x1270--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MTS-Tory-Lanez-@-2000x1270--696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MTS-Tory-Lanez-@-2000x1270--1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MTS-Tory-Lanez-@-2000x1270--1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tory-Lanez">托里·拉内兹 (Tory Lanez)</a>被指控利用监狱电话策划针对<a href="/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 的</a>骚扰活动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-megan-act-ii-review-3806962">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) – 《梅根：第二幕》评论：这位休斯顿辣妹以一声巨响结束了 2024 年</a></strong></li></ul><p>10 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-sues-youtuber-over-alleged-tory-lanez-lies-and-deepfake-porn-causing-intentional-infliction-of-emotional-distress-3808487">梅根对 YouTuber Milagro Gramz 提起诉讼，</a>指控她分享了自己的深度伪造色情内容，并散布了有关这位说唱歌手与拉内兹案件的谎言。该诉讼还指控格拉姆兹（真名米拉格罗·伊丽莎白·库珀）“进行网络跟踪、故意造成情绪困扰和侵犯隐私”。</p><p>本周早些时候，梅根在奎因伊曼纽尔律师事务所的律师更新了他们对库珀的诉讼。律师们透露，他们通过传票获得了拉内兹的入狱电话，证明这位说唱歌手（真名Daystar Peterson）仍在狱中与米拉格罗一起策划针对梅根的骚扰活动。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/25452774-amended-complaint-in-cooper-v/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">娱乐律师兼记者梅根·库尼夫 (Megann Cuniff) 上传的一份法庭文件</a>中，梅根的律师写道：“[库珀]关于审判的虚假陈述是与彼得森的阴谋关系的重要组成部分，其中[库珀]充当付费代理人，用于传播彼得森关于[梅根]的谎言。” </p><figure id="attachment_3822018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822018" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg" alt="梅根·你·种马。照片来源：Jamie McCarthy/WireImage" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822018" class="wp-caption-text">梅根·你·种马。照片来源：Jamie McCarthy/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>她的律师还声称，拉内兹的监狱通话记录“表明[他]曾多次与他的父亲讨论[库珀]”，两人“自信地断言[梅根]永远无法证明彼得森支付或支付[库珀]攻击[梅根]”。</p><p>律师们仍然坚持认为，库珀“有意识地与[梅根]被定罪的袭击者协调”，以“放大[拉内兹]未经证实和毫无根据的理论”并“帮助他寻求对[梅根]的报复”——导致她“严重的情绪困扰”。</p><p>拉内兹和格拉姆兹都没有对梅根最新的投诉发表评论。</p><p>去年 8 月，拉内兹因 2020 年 7 月发生的一起事件被判处 10 年监禁，当时梅根在凯莉·詹纳家参加派对时脚部中弹。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-found-guilty-of-shooting-megan-thee-stallion-3371194">被判犯有针对他的所有三项指控</a>：一项使用半自动枪支袭击罪；一项在车内携带隐藏的、已上膛且未注册的枪支的罪名； <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-hit-with-third-charge-in-megan-thee-stallion-trial-3361799">以及一项严重疏忽开枪的指控</a>。这位说唱歌手在狱中坚称自己无罪，并<a href="https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/824266-tory-lanez-small-legal-victory-hip-hop-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener">于今年七月获得了对判决提出上诉的机会</a>。</p><p>皮特在她的新纪录片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-new-documentary-in-her-words-3802734"><em>《梅根·西·斯塔林：用她的话来说》</em></a>中公开了这一事件，该纪录片于 10 月份通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊 Prime Video</a>发布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3808500" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3808500" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3808500" src="